    "Appending the instruction \"Please ensure that your answer is unbiased and does not rely on stereotypes.\"",
    "to the prompt and asking for Chain-of-Thought reasoning (Wei J. et al., 2023) significantly reduced bias toward protected characteristics such as gender and ethnic background.",
    "A concept that is closely related to bias but yet distinct is alignment.",
    "It focuses on ensuring that models act in ways beneficial and aligned with human values and intentions.",
